Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.72,0:00:03.80,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh what is this palace life?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.70,0:00:08.85,Extra,,0,0,0,,That'll teach you to sneer at a nobleman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.85,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh my dear girl. What's been done to you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.85,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Somebody cut off my ear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.77,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Because they didn't like my face.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.85,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,But that's barbaric!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.62,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's home.\N[Arabian Nights]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.25,0:00:23.47,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Well, worry not, miss. I am a studied healer.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to save the ear, but I can stay the bleeding.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Ahm, it would help if we kept you talking.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,You could start by telling me your name.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.10,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,My name is Shahrazad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.55,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I suppose this will be the end of me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.60,0:00:39.72,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I'm here only for my beauty and - now that's gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.72,0:00:43.07,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Shahrazad, true beauty lies within.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.07,0:00:46.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,But no scratch could tarnish your heavenly glow.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.45,0:00:51.72,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,*Sigh* Your words are like honey, young master.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.37,0:00:54.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jaffar. And I am master to no man or woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.40,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I am a servant to the people and therefore your servant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.82,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,*Sigh*
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.02,0:01:04.32,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Tell me, ahm - what is it that you do in the palace?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.32,0:01:08.25,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I entertain nobels with singing and dancing and...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.62,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,...stories
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.30,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Stories? What kind of stories?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.47,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Oh, of anything you can image.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.47,0:01:18.50,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Tell me, have you ever heard the tale of the tiger head cave?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.10,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Filled with wonders beyond your wildest dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.10,0:01:25.50,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,A forbidden treasure. A rug possessed with the soul of a lecherous thief?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.70,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,And perhaps the greatest treasure of them all:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.45,0:01:31.60,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,A common oil lamp!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.90,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,What?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.65,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Oh, but do not be fooled by it's common-place appearance.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.30,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary lamp.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.40,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,It is the prison of a djinn.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.67,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,A shapeshifter who will grant your every wish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.72,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,He's also really funny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.15,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Well, there we are. Keep the bandages tight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.50,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Let's the wounds become - gangrenes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.17,0:02:01.25,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,By Allah! Are you a sorcerer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.25,0:02:04.77,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh no! No! Sorcery is a craft for fools and dreamers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.77,0:02:09.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I am a man of science. I believe only in what I can touch and feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.20,0:02:13.07,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,This cave you speak of: I can assure you it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.12,0:02:19.12,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I would know because - I apprenticed a geographer
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.52,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Oh you've just never seen it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.52,0:02:27.17,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Because the cave remains hidden to all but those who posses the key.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.52,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Here, look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.40,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,A beautiful pendant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.87,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,A golden scarab if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.87,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Half a scarab - half the key.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.62,0:02:41.17,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,It is said that the cave was sealed by two lovers...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.17,0:02:44.32,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,...who were then transformed into one golden scarab.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.82,0:02:48.07,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,The cave will only reopen when the two halves become one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.42,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,The lovers are united once more.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.52,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.07,0:02:57.27,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,So you see - You say you only believe what you can touch and feel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.82,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Magic does nothing if not touch the soul.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.47,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,And there's no greater feeling than that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.10,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Wise words.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.10,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.07,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.42,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I have been touched.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:28.07,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Ah, pardon. You  know many stories, do you?
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.67,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,start of song
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.67,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I know a thousand tales
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.07,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,To fill a thousand nights
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.40,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,But now another story comes to mind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:42.60,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,A noble young Vizier - ascends to wondrous heights
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.35,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,He's brilliant as he's handsome
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.02,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,And handsome as he's kind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:53.82,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,He is at once familiar and unknowable
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.62,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,To the frightened girl he meets along the way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.12,0:04:04.85,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,And to the girl's surprise - something in his eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.85,0:04:11.30,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Beckons her to know him and inspires her to say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.02,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I want to know your story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.32,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I want to know your past
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.32,0:04:21.72,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,So tell me slowly from the start
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.25,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Leave out no detail
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.17,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Savour every part
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.47,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I want to know your story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.45,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,So make the story last
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.45,0:04:38.80,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I want to know each twist and turn
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.02,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Tell me all I've missed
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.70,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I've so much to learn
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.32,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,For when it comes to stories
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.05,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew them all
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.25,0:04:58.62,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Now I'm face to face with one I can't seem to recall
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:06.55,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,The young vizier had come - to help inspire change
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:11.17,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,But fate had planned an unexpected twist
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:16.77,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Within the palace walls he discovered something strange
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.77,0:05:23.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,And found the missing part of him he didn't know he'd missed
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:28.65,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,She is at once a comfort and a mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.07,0:05:33.15,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,To the callow man she meets that fateful day
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.15,0:05:36.10,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,She's beautiful and wise
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.07,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,And something in her eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.07,0:05:45.50,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Beckons him to know her and inspires him to say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.17,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I want to know your story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.47,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I want to know your past
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.47,0:05:55.62,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I want to know your future too
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.57,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Fill my days and nights
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,With the tale of you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.27,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I want to know your story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.77,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I want to know your story
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.35,0:06:08.17,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,So make the story last
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.45,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Make the story-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.15,0:06:12.17,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,And linger over every part
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.10,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Tell it till I know
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.97,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Every bit by heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.77,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I never cared for stories
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Until you entered mine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.72,0:06:30.25,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,And now my only wish is that our plots may intertwine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.55,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,But I forget what happens next
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.65,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I understand
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.65,0:06:44.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Remind me how she answers when he asks her for her hand
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.97,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:54.15,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,A thousand and one nights with you is not enough to spend
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.15,0:06:59.07,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,So let's make ours a story with no end
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:05.65,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,So let's make ours a story with no end
Comment: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:05.65,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,End of song
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.12,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Honey, I'm home. Oh, damn that royal Vizier!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.12,0:07:14.55,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,The common man is starving and he feasts like a self styled god.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.95,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,My land reform bill will never pass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.35,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,They refused you again?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.35,0:07:22.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,I work with the most selfish, corrupt, incompetent old men...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.10,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,...their mouths aren't fit to hold a donkey's shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.85,0:07:30.70,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,If I could just speak with the sultan! If for a minute I could have his ear!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.70,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,As that nobleman took my ear?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.97,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Shahrazad, you jest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.97,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I'm only joking, Jaffar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.60,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Now that I have got you smiling, I think I'll give you a gift.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.97,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,A gift for me? What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.97,Bird,,0,0,0,,*Bird croak*
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.65,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh what a handsome bird that is!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.00,Bird,,0,0,0,,*Croak* Handsome bird.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.27,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh it speaks our words.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.27,0:07:56.12,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,I saw him in the marketplace and I knew he would delight you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.52,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh what else does he say?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.30,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,Anything you teach him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.07,Bird,,0,0,0,,*Croak* Donkey shit.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.55,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh, those harsh words are mine, aren't they?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.50,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,You clever girl. Always finding new ways to keep me honest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.52,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,It'll be good for us to have something to love and care for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.52,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,It can be practice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.60,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,For us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.77,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Have all of our attempts finally bore fruit?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.65,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Even when the doctor said it could not be so?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.65,0:08:27.92,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Oh praise Allah! The merciful and compassionate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.97,Messenger,,0,0,0,,Assistant Vizier Jaffar! News from the palace.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.75,Messenger,,0,0,0,,Your request for a hearing with the sultan has been granted.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.52,Messenger,,0,0,0,,You are to report to the palace immediately!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.70,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,You hear that, my darling?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:42.02,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,My land reform bill being heard by the sultan on this of all days!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.55,Shahrazad,,0,0,0,,We're blessed, Jaffar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.50,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Come with me to the palace and let us never be parted again.
Comment: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:54.47,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,Start of song
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:54.47,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,A thousand and one nights with you is not enough to spend
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:09:00.20,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,So let's make ours a story with no end
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.75,0:09:09.72,Jaffar,,0,0,0,,So let's make ours a story with no end
